    "en": {
      "title": "Gotabaya did not seek asylum in Singapore",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Singapore has confirmed that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has visited Singapore on a personal visit, and said that he has not sought asylum there."
